<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.6">
<l>etticai yumama rarpaṇin tēttum iruṭī kē caṉvaliceyya</l>
<l>muttaṉṉa veṇmuṟu vaṟceyya vāyum mulaiyu maḻakaḻin tēṉāṉ</l>
<l>kottalar kāvil maṇittaṭam kaṇpaṭai koḷḷu miḷaṅkuyi lēyeṉ</l>
<l>tattuva ṉaivarak kūkiṟṟi yākiṟ ṟalaiyallāl kaimmāṟi lēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The beauty of my pearl-like white teeth, red lips, and breasts have been ruined</l>
<l>as Hṛṣīkeśa—whom the immortals pay homage to and praise from all quarters—</l>
<l rend="indent">causes [me] pain.</l>
<l>O young koel that sleep in a beautiful place in the grove where clusters [of</l>
<l rend="indent">flowers] bloom!</l>
<l>if you cry so that my true [Lord] comes, I will [give] nothing [less than my] head in return!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
